<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Hermann Truchsess von Diessenhofen</head><p>Der Rat bittet erneut um Herausgabe der Sensen des Herdegen Valzner, Bürger zu Nürnberg.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_213" id="105r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_213_r2l24"><expan>H<ex>er</ex>man</expan> Truchſeſſen von Diſſenhofen </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_213_r2l25"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> her Truchſeſʒ / Als wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> vormals <expan>geſchrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_213_r2l26"><expan>gebete<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / von der Senſen <expan>vvege<ex>n</ex></expan> / 
<del rend="strikethrough"> als </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_213_line_1575977304705_921">dıe </ab></add> dem Herdegen valcʒner </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_213_r2l27"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>lıeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> <expan>aufgehalte<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd <expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan> ſein <expan>worde<ex>n</ex></expan>
<add><ab facs="#facs_213_r1l1">Alſo hat vns der </ab><ab facs="#facs_213_r1l2"><expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> aber </ab><ab facs="#facs_213_r1l3"><expan>furg<ex>eben</ex></expan> vvıe daʒ Jm </ab><ab facs="#facs_213_r1l4"><expan>dıeſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſein <expan>Senſe<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab><ab facs="#facs_213_r1l5">noch niht vvıder </ab><ab facs="#facs_213_r1l6"><expan>vvorde<ex>n</ex></expan> ſein / </ab></add>
<del rend="strikethrough"> vnd dıe Jr </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_213_r2l28">
<del rend="strikethrough">gen Diſſenhofen braht habt / Alſo <expan>bıte<ex>n</ex></expan> vvir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> erber / daʒ Jr Jm </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_213_line_1575977412661_954">
<del rend="strikethrough"> dıe 
<add><ab facs="#facs_213_line_1575977316025_931">
<del rend="strikethrough">von ew </del></ab></add> noch nicht <expan>wıdergeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<add><ab facs="#facs_213_r2l29">
<del rend="strikethrough">wıder vvorden ſein </del></ab></add> vnd <expan>geantvv<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> habt / Alſo </del> <expan>Bite<ex>n</ex></expan> vvir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_213_r2l34"><expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> mıt <expan>alle<ex>m</ex></expan> fleiſſe / daʒ Jr 
<add><ab facs="#facs_213_line_1575977310492_926">
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>d<ex>ur</ex>h</expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>ern</ex></expan> <expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> </del></ab></add> dem <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> <expan>dieſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_213_r2l35">ſein Senſen noch 
<del rend="strikethrough">on </del> <expan>vnu<ex>er</ex>cʒogenlıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>wıdergeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd onhındernüſſe </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_213_r2l36">volgen <expan>laſſe<ex>n</ex></expan> wollet <expan>d<ex>ur</ex>h</expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> Als etc / das <expan>wolle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_213" id="105r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>man</expan> Truchsessen von Dissenhofen </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> her Truchsesz, als wir
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> vormals <expan>geschrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        und <expan>gebete<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> von der sensen <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan>,
                            <add>die</add> dem Herdegen Valczner, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>lieb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>, <expan>aufgehalte<ex>n</ex></expan> und
                                <expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan> sein <expan>worde<ex>n</ex></expan>;
                            <add>also hat uns der <expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan>,
                                    <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>, aber <expan>furg<ex>eben</ex></expan>,
                            wie daz im <expan>dieselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> sein
                                <expan>sense<ex>n</ex></expan> noch niht wider
                                    <expan>worde<ex>n</ex></expan> sein</add>.
                            <expan>Bite<ex>n</ex></expan> wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> mit <expan>alle<ex>m</ex></expan> fleisse, daz
                        ir dem <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>, <expan>dieselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> sein
                        sensen noch <expan>unv<ex>er</ex>czogenlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>widergeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und onhindernüsse volgen
                                <expan>lasse<ex>n</ex></expan> wollet <expan>d<ex>ur</ex>h</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan>, als etc. Das <expan>wolle<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        etc.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
